{{Infobox dungeon |name = Mt. Chimney |image = [[File:Mt. Chimney.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Mt. Chimney. |tokens = 20,000 |location = North of Route 112, east of Lavaridge Town. }} '''Mt. Chimney''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Hoenn]]. It initially has 49 tiles arranged in a 7x7 square, including 7 chest tiles, 17 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
